#. Tag: title
#: resourceeditor.docbook:2
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Description</title>"
msgstr "<title>Opis</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:3
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Resource Editor is used to create, edit, and delete resources and "
"resource groups. Resources must belong to a resource group. At the moment "
"sub-groups are not allowed."
msgstr ""
"Urejevalnik virov se uporablja za ustvarjanje, urejanje in brisanje virov in "
"skupin virov. Viri morajo pripadati skupini virov. Podskupine trenutno niso "
"dovoljene."

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:19
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Working resources must refer to a <emphasis>calendar</emphasis> that defines "
"the working hours for the resource. Calendars are created using the <link "
"linkend=\"work-and-vacation-editor\">Work and Vacation Editor</link>."
msgstr ""
"Delovni viri se morajo nanašati na <emphasis>koledar</emphasis>, ki določa "
"delovne ure za vir. Koledarji so ustvarjeni z <link linkend=\"work-and-"
"vacation-editor\">urejevalnikom dela in počitnic</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Material resources are by default always available. You can use a calendar "
"to limit its availability."
msgstr ""
"Materialni viri so privzeto vedno na voljo. S koledarjem lahko omejite "
"njegovo razpoložljivost."

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:23
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Resources can be <emphasis>Shared</emphasis> or <emphasis>Local</emphasis>. "
"A local resource is only used in the current project. A shared resource can "
"be shared between multiple projects and is stored in a separate file, see "
"<link linkend=\"managing-resources\">Managing Resources</link>."
msgstr ""
"Viri so lahko <emphasis>v skupni rabi</emphasis> ali <emphasis>lokalni</"
"emphasis>. Lokalni vir se uporablja samo v trenutnem projektu. Skupni vir je "
"lahko v skupni rabi med več projekti in je shranjen v ločeni datoteki, "
"glejte <link linkend=\"managing-resources\">Upravljanje virov</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: resourceeditor.docbook:26
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toolbar"
msgstr "Orodna vrstica"

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:27
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The toolbar provides the means to create and delete resources and resource "
"groups:"
msgstr ""
"Orodna vrstica nudi sredstva za ustvarjanje in brisanje virov in skupin "
"virov:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: resourceeditor.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid "Button"
msgstr "Gumb"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: resourceeditor.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shortcut"
msgstr "Bližnjica"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: resourceeditor.docbook:36 resourceeditor.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Description</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Opis</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid "Add Resource Group"
msgstr "Dodaj skupino virov"

#. Tag: keycombo
#: resourceeditor.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;<keycap>I</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;<keycap>I</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Button to create a resource group. The new group is appended at the end of "
"the groups."
msgstr ""
"Gumb za ustvarjanje skupine virov. Nova skupina je dodana na koncu skupin."

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid "Add Resource"
msgstr "Dodaj vir"

#. Tag: keycombo
#: resourceeditor.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>I</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>I</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Button to create a resource. The new resource is appended as a child to the "
"currently selected group. If a resource is selected, the new resource is "
"appended to its parent group."
msgstr ""
"Gumb za ustvarjanje vira. Nov vir je kot podrejeni pripet trenutno izbrani "
"skupini. Če je izbran vir, se novi vir doda svoji nadrejeni skupini."

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Delete</para>"
msgstr "<para>Izbriši</para>"

#. Tag: keycap
#: resourceeditor.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>Delete</keycap>"
msgstr "<keycap>Izbriši</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid "Deletes the selected resources and/or resource groups."
msgstr "Izbriše izbrane vire in/ali skupine virov."

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Resources can be created by dropping data from any application that supports "
"dragging vCard information, like <emphasis>KAddressBook</emphasis> or "
"<emphasis>Evolution</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"Vire lahko ustvarite tako, da spustite podatke iz katere koli aplikacije, ki "
"podpira vlečenje informacij vCard, na primer <emphasis>KAddressBook</"
"emphasis> ali <emphasis>Evolution</emphasis>."

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Resources can be copied or moved to a different resource group using drag-"
"and-drop."
msgstr ""
"Vire je mogoče kopirati ali premakniti v drugo skupino virov s tehniko "
"povleci in spusti."

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid "When moving a resource, the resource will lose any allocations."
msgstr "Pri premikanju vira bo t vir izgubil vse dodelitve."

#. Tag: title
#: resourceeditor.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editing data"
msgstr "Urejanje podatkov"

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Data can be edited inline as described <link linkend=\"using-the-views"
"\">here</link>."
msgstr ""
"Podatke je mogoče urejati neposredno, kot je opisano <link linkend=\"using-"
"the-views\">tukaj</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "Resources can also be edited using the Resource Settings Dialog."
msgstr "Vire lahko urejate tudi v pogovornem oknu za nastavitve virov."

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid "The following columns are displayed as default:"
msgstr "Naslednji stolpci so privzeto prikazani:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: resourceeditor.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid "Column"
msgstr "Stolpec"

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid "Name"
msgstr "Ime"

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid "The name of the resource or resource group."
msgstr "Ime vira ali skupine virov."

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scope"
msgstr "Obseg"

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A resource can be <emphasis>Shared</emphasis> or <emphasis>Local</emphasis>. "
"A shared resource cannot be edited."
msgstr ""
"Vir je lahko <emphasis>v skupni rabi</emphasis> ali <emphasis>lokalni</"
"emphasis>. Skupnega vira ni mogoče urejati."

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid "Type"
msgstr "Vrsta"

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid "The type of resource or resource group."
msgstr "Vrsta vira ali skupine virov."

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid "Initials"
msgstr "Začetnice"

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid "The initials of the resource."
msgstr "Začetnice vira."

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid "Email"
msgstr "E-naslov"

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid "The e-mail address of the resource."
msgstr "E-poštni naslov vira."

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid "Calendar"
msgstr "Koledar"

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid "The calendar defines when the resource is working."
msgstr "Koledar določa, kdaj vir deluje."

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:150
#, no-c-format
msgid "Limit (%)"
msgstr "Omejitev (%)"

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid "The maximum load that can be assigned."
msgstr "Največja obremenitev, ki jo je mogoče dodeliti."

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:158
#, no-c-format
msgid "Available From"
msgstr "Na voljo od"

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:161 resourceeditor.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid "Defines when the resource is available to the project."
msgstr "Določa, kdaj je vir na voljo projektu."

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:166
#, no-c-format
msgid "Available Until"
msgstr "Na voljo do"

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:174
#, no-c-format
msgid "Normal Rate"
msgstr "Normalna cena"

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:177
#, no-c-format
msgid "The cost per hour, normal hours."
msgstr "Cena na uro, normalne ure."

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:182
#, no-c-format
msgid "Account"
msgstr "Račun"

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid "The account where the resource cost is accumulated."
msgstr "Račun, na katerem se zbirajo stroški vira."

#. Tag: title
#: resourceeditor.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija"

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using the context menu, the view can be configured to split/unsplit the tree "
"view or it can be configured using the configure dialog."
msgstr ""
"S kontekstnim menijem lahko pogled konfigurirate tako, da razdeli/razdeli "
"drevesni pogled, ali pa ga konfigurirate s pogovornim oknom za konfiguracijo."

#. Tag: para
#: resourceeditor.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The configure dialog enables you to tailor the amount of information the "
"view displays to fit your needs."
msgstr ""
"Konfiguracijsko pogovorno okno vam omogoča, da količino informacij, ki jih "
"prikaže pogled, prilagodite svojim potrebam."
